{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"证明毕达哥拉斯定理","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Examples/MathML_Pythagorean_Theorem","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","hasMathML":true,"sidebarHTML":"\n    <ol>\n        <li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element\">MathML Reference</a></strong>\n\n        \n            </li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/maction\">&lt;maction&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\">&lt;math&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/menclose\">&lt;menclose&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/merror\">&lt;merror&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfenced\">&lt;mfenced&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfrac\">&lt;mfrac&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mi\">&lt;mi&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mmultiscripts\">&lt;mmultiscripts&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mn\">&lt;mn&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mover\">&lt;mover&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mpadded\">&lt;mpadded&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mphantom\">&lt;mphantom&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mroot\">&lt;mroot&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mrow\">&lt;mrow&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/ms\">&lt;ms&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msqrt\">&lt;msqrt&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstyle\">&lt;mstyle&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msub\">&lt;msub&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msubsup\">&lt;msubsup&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msup\">&lt;msup&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtd\">&lt;mtd&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtext\">&lt;mtext&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtr\">&lt;mtr&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munder\">&lt;munder&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munderover\">&lt;munderover&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/semantics\">&lt;semantics&gt;</a></li>\n        \n\n        \n    </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>现在，我们来证明毕达哥拉斯定理（勾股定理）：</p>\n<p><strong>命题</strong>：在一个直角三角形中，斜边的平方等于其他两边的平方之和。</p>\n<p>例如，设 a 和 b 为两直角边，c 为斜边，那么 \n  <math>\n    <mrow>\n      <msup>\n        <mi>a </mi>\n        <mn>2</mn>\n      </msup>\n      <mo>+ </mo>\n      <msup>\n        <mi>b </mi>\n        <mn>2</mn>\n      </msup>\n      <mo>= </mo>\n      <msup>\n        <mi>c </mi>\n        <mn>2</mn>\n      </msup>\n    </mrow>\n  </math>。\n</p>\n<p>*<strong>*证明：**</strong> 我们可以通过代数证明来展示大正方形面积等于内正方形（斜边的平方）加上四个三角形的面积：</p>\n<p>\n  <math style=\"display: block;\">\n    <mtable columnalign=\"right center left\">\n      <mtr>\n        <mtd>\n          <msup>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>( </mo>\n              <mi>a </mi>\n              <mo>+ </mo>\n              <mi>b </mi>\n              <mo>) </mo>\n            </mrow>\n            <mn>2 </mn>\n          </msup>\n        </mtd>\n        <mtd>\n          <mo>= </mo>\n        </mtd>\n        <mtd>\n          <msup>\n            <mi>c </mi>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </msup>\n          <mo>+ </mo>\n          <mn>4 </mn>\n          <mo>⋅ </mo>\n          <mo>(</mo>\n          <mfrac>\n            <mn>1 </mn>\n            <mn>2 </mn>\n          </mfrac>\n          <mi>a </mi>\n          <mi>b </mi>\n          <mo>)</mo>\n        </mtd>\n      </mtr>\n      <mtr>\n        <mtd>\n          <msup>\n            <mi>a </mi>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </msup>\n          <mo>+ </mo>\n          <mn>2 </mn>\n          <mi>a </mi>\n          <mi>b </mi>\n          <mo>+ </mo>\n          <msup>\n            <mi>b </mi>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </msup>\n        </mtd>\n        <mtd>\n          <mo>= </mo>\n        </mtd>\n        <mtd>\n          <msup>\n            <mi>c </mi>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </msup>\n          <mo>+ </mo>\n          <mn>2 </mn>\n          <mi>a </mi>\n          <mi>b</mi>\n        </mtd>\n      </mtr>\n      <mtr>\n        <mtd></mtd>\n      </mtr>\n      <mtr>\n        <mtd>\n          <msup>\n            <mi>a </mi>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </msup>\n          <mo>+ </mo>\n          <msup>\n            <mi>b </mi>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </msup>\n        </mtd>\n        <mtd>\n          <mo>= </mo>\n        </mtd>\n        <mtd>\n          <msup>\n            <mi>c </mi>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </msup>\n        </mtd>\n      </mtr>\n    </mtable>\n  </math>\n</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"现在，我们来证明毕达哥拉斯定理（勾股定理）：","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Proving the Pythagorean theorem","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"MathML Pythagorean Theorem","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Preuve du théorème de Pythagore","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"ピタゴラスの定理の証明","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Доказательство теоремы Пифагора","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/mathml/examples/mathml_pythagorean_theorem","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/mathml/examples/mathml_pythagorean_theorem/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML","title":"MathML"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Examples","title":"举个例子"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Examples/MathML_Pythagorean_Theorem","title":"证明毕达哥拉斯定理"}],"pageTitle":"证明毕达哥拉斯定理 - MathML | MDN","noIndexing":false}}